<item>
 <title>Remarkable Life</title>
 <link>http://assorted.in/commentaire/remarkable-life</link>
 <description>&lt;p&gt;I read the following definition of &#039;Remarkable Life&#039; on this &lt;a href=&quot;http://calnewport.com/blog/2009/07/22/does-living-a-remarkable-life-require-courage-or-effort/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;link&lt;/a&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;cite&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
A remarkable life is one in which: (1) you do something meaningful that you enjoy; (2) you have a flexible schedule that you control; and (3) you earn recognition and good (enough) compensation.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;/cite&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It is not too far off the mark.&lt;/p&gt;
