<item>
 <title>Fire And Motion</title>
 <link>http://assorted.in/commentaire/fire-and-motion</link>
 <description>&lt;p&gt;Ever felt, what the heck am i doing? Am i going somewhere? Am i on the path of achieving whatever i would like to? And i am not writing this in parlance of only the professional career. This includes the personal goals one might have for themselves e.g. learning to play a musical instrument, running a marathon, learning foreign languages, helping out community, writing a book etc.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;These thoughts do tend to cross once a while in my mind, and for me at least, the reason is an overt need of achieving targets (or measurable goals) at a reasonably fast pace. I tend to get a touch restless, if things are not happening quick enough or in some cases not happening at all.&lt;/p&gt;
